pageTitle: Lexington Wall Sconce by Tech Lighting | 700wslexcz
textBeforeTable: Lexington Wall Sconce features a half-cylinder fabric shade with rolled edges and minimal metal base. Shade available in Desert Clay or White with finish in Satin Nickel or Antique Bronze. Fixture available with halogen, compact fluorescent or LED lamp option. Halogen includes one 60 watt, 120 volt, BT15 medium base halogen lamp. Compact fluorescent version includes one 18 watt, 120 volt, T5 2G11 base twin tube compact fluorescent lamp and non-dimmable electronic ballast. LED version includes two 120 volt, 10 watt 2700K color temperature LED modules, 600 lumens. ETL listed. ADA compliant. 7.1 inch width x 14.1 inch height x 3.3 inch depth. The Tech brand has since evolved, with a portfolio offering an expansive selection of lighting solutions for both residential and commercial applications. Tech Lighting products span a wide variety of lighting categories, including low- and line-voltage decorative pendants, wall sconces, chandeliers, bath bars and bath lighting, picture lights, directional track heads and ceiling fixtures (both flush mount and suspension) all featuring timeless, original design.
